postWorkshop.body:
Hi {firstName},

Thanks for joining the workshop. Here's everything in one place:

**Your workshop recording**: {recordingLink}
**Workspace setup**: {quickstartLink}
**Community**: {communityLink}

If you shipped a workflow today, we'd love to hear what you built. Hit reply and tell us.

**If you want to go deeper**: The next Dogfooding Cohort opens {cohortDate}. Details and enrollment: {cohortLink}

— Jai

