runFailed.body:
Hi {firstName},

Your {workflowName} workflow ran at {time} and didn't complete.

**What happened**: {briefReason}
**See full details**: {runDetailLink}

If this keeps happening, come find us in the community or reply to this email.

— TryDogfooding

budgetWarning50.body:
Hi {firstName},

Heads up: you've used ${used} of your ${cap} monthly cap.

No action needed — this is normal mid-month. We'll warn you again at 80%, and stop runs if you hit 100%.

**See usage**: {usageLink}
**Change your cap**: {settingsLink}

— TryDogfooding

budgetWarning80.body:
Hi {firstName},

You've used ${used} of your ${cap} monthly cap.

At 100% we'll pause workflow runs until next month or until you raise the cap.

**See usage**: {usageLink}
**Raise your cap**: {settingsLink}

— TryDogfooding

